VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (api[_-]?key|secret|token|password)\s*[:=]\s*[\'\"][^\'\"]{8,}[\'\"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|placeholder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely hardcoded secrets in NativeScript projects.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for NativeScript Hardcoded Secret Marker.
